2. Real stems are never wired in. The AudioEngine currently SYNTHESIZES stems (oscillators per synthKey). It must instead fetch+decode the real mp3 stems into AudioBuffers. Rework engine load path; drop/bypass synthesis for these songs.
3. songs.js must be replaced with the 3 real songs: real title, bpm (HWHMF=96, GTG=97), key, and section/cue timings derived from the actual tracks (not the old fictional 8-bar synth math).
